---
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
import Cta from "@/components/cta.astro";
import Features from "@/components/features.astro";
import Hero from "@/components/hero.astro";
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="">
  <Container>
    <Hero />
    <section class="mt-20 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr] lg:items-start">
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight text-navy-900">
        Helping You Build Your Future in Canada
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-navy-600">
        <p>
          At SCVI Immigration Law, we understand that every immigration journey is unique. Whether you're looking to study, work, reunite with family, or establish permanent residence in Canada, our goal is to provide clear, reliable guidance that helps you move forward with confidence.
        </p>
        <p>
          We are committed to delivering personalized immigration services tailored to each client's individual circumstances. By taking the time to understand your goals, we develop thoughtful strategies and ensure that all IRCC submissions are handled end to end.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <Features />
    <section class="mt-20 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr] lg:items-start">
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight text-navy-900">
        Our Approach
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-navy-600">
        <p>
          At SCVI Immigration, we believe successful outcomes begin with understanding our clients' goals. We take a collaborative approach, carefully assessing each situation, explaining available pathways, and developing a strategy that aligns with your individual needs.
        </p>
        <p>
          From your initial consultation through application preparation, submission, and ongoing support, we are committed to providing timely communication, practical guidance, and professional representation. Our goal is to make the immigration process as straightforward and stress-free as possible, so you can focus on your future in Canada with confidence.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <Cta />
  </Container>
</Layout>
